sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client
    participant N as Nginx
    participant M as Middleware
    participant A as Auth
    participant W as WAF Service
    participant R as ML Registry
    participant D as PostgreSQL
    participant L as Alert Manager
    participant S as SIEM

    C->>N: POST /api/v1/waf/predict
    N->>M: HTTPS request
    M->>M: X-Request-ID
    M->>A: Validate JWT or API Key
    A->>D: Lookup credentials
    D-->>A: Principal
    M->>W: predict(payload)
    W->>R: Load active model
    R-->>W: joblib pipeline
    W->>W: TF-IDF + LogReg + rules
    W-->>M: WafPredictResult
    M-->>C: 200 JSON
    M->>L: emit alert
    par Fan-out
        L->>S: JSON or CEF webhook
    and
        L-->>C: WebSocket push
    end
